st info.  Now I'm sure we'll see more folks doing this quest as it's up on Allkhazam's!  Anyways, my real focus on this thread is in regards to Abrogast's mace.  It is 6/24 if I remember correctly and has 5 to Greater Akheva/Akheva.  Has anyone tested this out and found anything useful with the mace?  It is a +6wis +5sv_fire/sv_magic item nonetheless.  Could it be considered a decent cleric item?  I'm not sure...<br>
