<br>
A few tips:<br>
<br>
+ They both run decently fast; both were able to catch up to me just fine until snared.<br>
<br>
+ You can 'single pull' Abrogast first from the bank because Miller will exclaim &quot;wait for me!&quot; and take off running towards the bar but Abrogast will still be in the middle of buffing up.  That delay is enough to pull Abro solo without Miller even being near.<br>
<br>
+ Abro drops a No Drop mace:<br>
<br>
Shimmering Mace<br>
6/24<br>
Bane: Akheva, Greater Akheva +5<br>
Wis 6, Save Fire 5, Save Magic 5<br>
WAR, CLR, PAL, RNG, SHD, DRU, MNK, BRD, ROG, SHM<br>
Wt: 4.5<br>
<br>
+ Miller drops a pair of No Rent blades<br>
<br>
+ The necklace has the icon of the chitin shell shield from Upper Guk, kinda confusing at first glance.  It also has stats of its own including Wisdom, although I did not write those down. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ulasombracorazon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lasombra Corazon</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0> at: 12/22/01 3:49:34 pm<br></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showMessage?topicID=3345.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showMessage?topicID=2545.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3484.topic&index=93><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.emailToFriend?topicID=3484.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.threadControl?topicID=3484.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3484.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3484.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cel